test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (4 == 3)
 +  where 4 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x77b75e553140>([-7])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x77b75e553140> = [[1, -7], [1, -7, 1], [-7], [-7, 1], [1, -7], [1, -7, 1], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 7 == -7
 +  where 7 = <built-in function prod>([-1, -7])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
